CREATE TABLE rakamin-kf-analytics-423210.kimia_farma.kf_analisa AS SELECT f.transaction_id, f.date, f.branch_id, k.branch_name, k.kota, k.provinsi, k.rating AS rating_cabang, f.customer_name, f.product_id, p.product_name, p.price AS actual_price, f.discount_percentage, CASE WHEN f.price <= 50000 THEN 0.1 WHEN f.price > 50000 AND f.price <= 100000 THEN 0.15 WHEN f.price > 100000 AND f.price <= 300000 THEN 0.2 WHEN f.price > 300000 AND f.price <= 500000 THEN 0.25 WHEN f.price > 500000 THEN 0.3 END AS persentase_gross_laba, f.price - (f.price * f.discount_percentage) AS nett_sales, (f.price - (f.price * f.discount_percentage)) * ( CASE WHEN f.price <= 50000 THEN 0.1 WHEN f.price > 50000 AND f.price <= 100000 THEN 0.15 WHEN f.price > 100000 AND f.price <= 300000 THEN 0.2 WHEN f.price > 300000 AND f.price <= 500000 THEN 0.25 WHEN f.price > 500000 THEN 0.3 END) AS nett_profit, f.rating as rating_transaksi, FR
